Paglo,is,an,IT,management,company,Paglo,s,search,engine,for,IT,technology,automates,the,collection,of,all,of,your,IT,and,operations,data,and,ensures,that,you,can,instantly,solve,computer,network,and,user,problems,Use,Paglo,to,quickly,search,and,analyze,your,data,Paglo,supports,the,management,of,inventories,networks,servers,cloud,services,and,search,The,Paglo,API,supports,requests,from,computer,programs,from,both,Paglo,and,other,third,parties,You,can,write,small,scripts,and,programs,that,submit,data,to,the,Paglo,API,The,API,makes,it,easy,to,submit,PQL,queries,against,your,Paglo,database,and,to,add,documents,to,it